标题：灯台（lampstand）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מְנוֹרָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mnorah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:10\">2KI 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:2\">ZEC 4:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:11\">ZEC 4:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">兰：נֶבְרְשָׁה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：nevrshah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:5\">DAN 5:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：λυχνία</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：luchnia)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:15\">MAT 5:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:21\">MRK 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:16\">LUK 8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:33\">LUK 11:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:13\">REV 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:20\">REV 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:20\">REV 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:1\">REV 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:5\">REV 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:4\">REV 11:4</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/UBS-0029_lampstand.jpg\" alt=\"灯台\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">灯台 (© Deutsche Bibelgesellschaft, Stuttgart by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>灯台是用来托住一盏灯或一组灯的支架，可用多种材料做成，形状和大小也非常多样。使用灯台的目的是使灯盏高于地板或桌子，增大照明面积。关于帐幕中的灯台，参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.3.4 灯台 (lampstand, menorah)&lt;REALIA:4.3.4&gt;</a> 。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0941_oil_lamps.jpg\" alt=\"灯台上的油灯\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">灯台上的油灯 (© Zde Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>许多文化没有专指“灯台”的词语，因此这个词可能要译为“灯座”、“用来放灯的东西”或“放灯的地方”。如果翻译者将油灯译为“蜡烛”，那么可以使用一个表示烛台的词语。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:5\">DAN 5:5</a> ：这节经文提到墙上的字是在“灯台对面”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）。这是整个宴会厅中最亮的地方。在大多数语言中，翻译者可能都要清楚说明这一点，可译为“灯光最明亮的地方”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）、“灯光最强的地方”，或“人们看得非常清楚的地方”。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
